## Appearently nano has a configfile. And altough I despise this horrible piece
## of software, every now and then, I'm forced to used this monster.
## This file is all about damage control.


# Yay behaviour that vim has by default...
set const

# Yes why is that line there in the first place.
set morespace

# Holy shit. This has been annoying me for years...
unset nowrap
set smooth

# Again default vim behaviour
set smarthome

# Yeshhh, I really need to learn how make use of suspension.
set suspend

# OMG why isn't this default yet?
set tabsize 4
